rdf:Alt.rdf:li: #MMINAIL GitHub Pages Profile Banner Left Logo Position

This file renders a copy of the original MMINAIL Profile Banner in (.svg). The registered Logo Badge of the MMINAIL is postioned against the left margin of the banner. The background photo is a snap of the Tonto Cactus Forest east of Scottsdale facing the Four Peaks Wilderness Area pre-rio fire of '95.
